df_an <- df %>% filter(
  universe == "cognition",
  # and filter to literal for now, this is one reason to use patchwork
  agent_type == "literal",
)

df_natural <- df_an %>% filter(
  natural == TRUE
)

df_dominant <- df_an %>% filter(
  dominant == TRUE
)
(
  ggplot(
    df_an,
    aes(
      x=complexity,
      y=comm_cost,
    )
  )
  # dominant
  + geom_point(
    data = df_dominant,
    color = "black",
  )
  # all langs
  + geom_point(
    aes(
      color = iff,
    ),
    alpha=0.1,
  )
  # natural
  + geom_point(
    data = df_natural,
    shape = "+",
    color = "red",
  )
  + scale_color_viridis(option = "cividis")
  + facet_grid("prior ~ utility")
)
